metadata.name: Time Switch #46
metadata.description:
Press "S" to save a 2000x2000 png of your iteration

"Time Switch" 
The idea is sometimes we get too busy in stuff or we get too stuck with something and end up losing ourselves... Sometime all we need is a reminder, a motivation or simply a direction. The time can represent a good moment, or simply a moment for yourself, a minute to feel good , the wording can be encouragement, a reminder, an aim, a passion, a direction and backed by beautiful patterns and calm or vibrant colors it can be eye-catching.

Its a piece of art with precise time, a lot of motivational and fun quotes, 360 degrees of generative art, with 48 unique color schemes and a lot of variances in patterns, it has a variety of intriguing generative art pieces which should refresh you.

metadata.name: FxOscope #67
metadata.description:
Fxoscope is the first design of the Tinker Series. Fundemantal principle behind the series will be the motional complexities and orbital designs. Microstructures such as cellular movement and flowfield designs are also other fundamentals of the series.

Mouse click starts and stops the FxOscope.

Live is also recommended!

Relationship between macrocosmos and microcosmos shines through a secret mirror, waiting to be discovered patiently. Every motion lefts a trace behind it to be part of a past and to give birth to many futures.

metadata.name: Grid Studies #194
metadata.description:
Grid Studies is part of the fxhash interactive minting experience at Proof of People, London 2022.

Press 1, 2, 3 or 4 to change the pixel density, press ’s’ to save as PNG.

metadata.name: Flower Arrangement #74
metadata.description:
Flower arrangement made by code.

Possible features:
- Style: Natural, Oval, Triangular, Grassy
- Orientation: Square, Portrait, Landscape
- Palette: White, Cream, Tan, Pink, Green, Blue, Yellow, Orange
- Primary flower: Mix, Gerbera, Gerbera 2, Dahlia, Dahlia 2, Spiky, Unknown
- Primary color: Random, Light, Dark
- Secondary color: Random, Light, Dark
- Vase shape: Cylinder, Tumbler, Round, Curve
- Dish: true, false
- Table: true, false
- Texture: true, false

Live view options:
- Press "s" key: Saves the high resolution image (3300 x 3300 for square, 4200 x 3300 for portrait, 3300 x 4200 for landscape)

Depending on the device you run it on, it may take some time for the drawing to complete.
Best viewed in larger window size.
Made with p5js.

August 2022
ykxotkx
